snippet.title: We Wish You A Merry Christmas USA - Nintendo Wii
snippet.description:
This was recorded from Tnavigator gameplay. Game title is in the end of the video.

Tnavigator is a emulator app designed for Xbox One/Series models, and Windows 10 PC's. 

Please check it out the demonstration and users reviews here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WmutT...
